    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level of 3 due to single-condition ASTM F1717 testing; this shortfall is accepted given that the single condition is the FDA-mandated standard configuration and the model influence is Medium. Overall credibility is sufficient for the intended 510(k) regulatory submission at Medium assurance level.",
